top, a tree collapses and knocks down the wall; the survivors defend the community from an invasion of walkers. As it is believed that the tree was knocked over by the Whisperers, Lydia is attacked by a group of Alexandrians; Negan saves her, accidentally killing one of the attackers in the process. The council is conflicted on what to do with Negan, but Negan goes missing, putting the community on high alert. A depressed Ezekiel nearly attempts [[suicide]], but Michonne intervenes. Michonne, Judith, Luke, and others travel to Oceanside to help the community with walkers.\n| LineColor       = A51C36\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|The Walking Dead (season 10)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 136\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n| Title           = [[What It Always Is]]\n| DirectedBy      = Laura Belsey\n| WrittenBy       = Eli Jorn\u00e9\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|11|3}}\n| Viewers         = 3.09<ref name=\"10.05\">{{cite web |url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/sunday-cable-ratings-nov-3-2019/ |title=Sunday cable ratings: NFL leads, \u2018The Walking Dead\u2019 slips again |work=TV by the Numbers |first=Alex |last=Welch |date=November 5, 2019 |accessdate=November 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = Kelly becomes disoriented due to her hearing loss and gets lost in the woods, but is later found by Daryl, Connie, and Magna. Aaron encounters Gamma and offers her bandages after she cuts her hand; Gamma flees and informs Alpha of their interaction. Negan is found and joined by Brandon; Brandon murders a mother and her son in an effort to impress Negan, leading Negan to kill him. At Hilltop, the community works to rebuild the wall, while Ezekiel reveals to Siddiq that he has [[thyroid cancer]]. Magna reveals to Yumiko that she killed a man who attacked her young cousin, causing a rift between the two. Negan crosses into the Whisperers' territory and is attacked by Beta.\n| LineColor       = A51C36\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|The Walking Dead (season 10)\n| EpisodeNum