eb.archive.org/web/20200127090603/http://wjw.ah.gov.cn/news_details_53944.html|archive-date=2020-01-27|access-date=}}</ref> Ningxia reported one additional laboratory-confirmed case.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wsjkw.nx.gov.cn/info/1140/13226.htm|title=\u5168\u533a\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u611f\u67d3\u7684\u80ba\u708e\u75ab\u60c5\u901a\u62a5|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129162002/http://wsjkw.nx.gov.cn/info/1140/13226.htm|archive-date=2020-01-29|access-date=}}</ref> Shanghai reported 13 additional laboratory-confirmed cases, bringing the total up to 33.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5632784|title=\u3010\u6f8e\u6e43\u653f\u52a1\u3011_\u6caa\u65b0\u589e13\u4f8b\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u611f\u67d3\u7684\u80ba\u708e\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b\uff01\u4e0a\u6d77\u94c1\u8def\u5c40\u3001\u5e02\u6c11\u653f\u5c40\u53d1\u5e03\u6700\u65b0\u901a\u77e5_\u6743\u5a01\u53d1\u5e03_\u6f8e\u6e43\u65b0\u95fb-ThePaper.cn|website=m.thepaper.cn|access-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125103150/https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5632784|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nJapan, South Korea, and the United States all confirmed their second cases.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-japan-idUSKBN1ZM35W|title=Japan confirms second case of Wuhan virus: health ministry|last=Gallagher|first=Chris|date=January 23, 2020|website=Reuters|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128090050/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-japan-idUSKBN1ZM35W|archive-date=January 28, 2020|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/asia/live-news/coronavirus-outbreak-hnk-intl-01-24-20/h_7df038a58420da0cb7769f22803cbcc8|title=Three cities under lockdown as coronavirus outbreak kills dozens in China|last=|first=|date=January 23, 2020|website=CNN|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|