us suspected cases tested negative.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.derstandard.at/story/2000113770946/gewissheit-zu-coronavirus-verdachtsfall-in-wien-erst-am-montag|title=Coronavirus: Zwei Personen negativ getestet, doch zwei neue Verdachtsf\u00e4lle|date=2020-01-27|work=derStandard|access-date=2020-01-27|language=de|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126221209/https://www.derstandard.at/story/2000113770946/gewissheit-zu-coronavirus-verdachtsfall-in-wien-erst-am-montag|archive-date=2020-01-26|url-status=live}}</ref> The '[[Matei Bal\u0219]]' Institute reported the first possible case in Romania.,<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/posibil-caz-de-coronavirus-in-romania-1251235|title=Posibil caz de coronavirus \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. Reac\u021bia Ministerului S\u0103n\u0103t\u0103\u021bii: \"Este foarte pu\u021bin probabil\"|date=2020-01-27|access-date=2020-01-27|language=ro|website=digi24.ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127154230/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/posibil-caz-de-coronavirus-in-romania-1251235|archive-date=2020-01-27|url-status=live}}</ref> but the first case would not be confirmed until 26 February.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23687251-primul-caz-infectie-coronavirus-confirmat-oficial-romania.htm|title=Primul caz de infec\u021bie cu coronavirus, confirmat oficial \u00een Rom\u00e2nia: Un b\u0103rbat din Gorj ce a intrat \u00een contact cu italianul care a vizitat recent \u021bara noastr\u0103|website=HotNews.ro|author=Neagu, Alina|date=26 February 2020|access-date=3 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226220952/https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23687251-primul-caz-infectie-coronavirus-confirmat-oficial-romania.htm|archive-date=26 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mediafax.ro/coronavirus/detalii-despre-primul-roman-diagnosticat-cu-noul-coronavirus-are-20-de-ani-si-lucra-la-restaurantul-italianului-care-a-vizita