ruary 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Ecuador reported a suspected case of coronavirus, a Chinese citizen who arrived from Hong Kong.,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ticotimes.net/2020/01/27/ecuador-reports-first-suspected-case-of-coronavirus|title=Ecuador reports first suspected case of coronavirus|website=The Tico Times Costa Rica|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127172129/https://ticotimes.net/2020/01/27/ecuador-reports-first-suspected-case-of-coronavirus|archive-date=2020-01-27|url-status=live}}</ref> but the first case would not be confirmed until 29 February.<ref name=ecuador.1>{{cite tweet|user=elcomerciocom|number=1233773816825946113|date=29 February 2020|title=Ministra de Salud confirma primer caso de #coronavirus en Ecuador.}}</ref> Fiji authorities are holding six Chinese travelers in quarantine in [[Nadi]] as a precaution after they failed to gain entry to Samoa due to Samoa's quarantine requirements that were implemented Friday. The quarantine requirements, imposed after an emergency Cabinet meeting, compel anyone who's been in China to \"self-quarantine\" in a country free from the coronavirus for 14 days.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/world/2020/01/pacific-nations-on-alert-for-coronavirus-6-quarantined-in-fiji.html|title=Pacific nations on alert for coronavirus, 6 quarantined in Fiji|work=Newshub|access-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127043627/https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/world/2020/01/pacific-nations-on-alert-for-coronavirus-6-quarantined-in-fiji.html|archive-date=2020-01-27|url-status=live}}</ref> In Poland, two children were admitted to the [[Krak\u00f3w]] hospital with the suspicion of coronavirus.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://krakow.wyborcza.pl/krakow/7,44425,25638900,do-krakowskiego-szpita-trafilo-dwoje-dzieci-z-podejrzeniem-koronawirusa.html|language=pl|website=krakow.wyborcza.pl|access-date=2020-01-27|date=2020-01-27|title=Dwoje dzieci ze \u015al\u010