one the reopening of schools.<ref name=\":14\">{{cite web|url=http://cnhubei.com/content/2020-01/29/content_12659024.html|title=\u6e56\u5317\u7701\u5404\u7c7b\u4f01\u4e1a\u590d\u5de5\u65f6\u95f4\u4e0d\u65e9\u4e8e2\u670813\u65e524\u65f6|language=zh|date=2020-01-29|website=cnhubei.com|accessdate=2020-01-29}}</ref>\n\nThe [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]] confirms its first case.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://gulfnews.com/uae/health/coronavirus-first-case-confirmed-in-uae-1.1580273983681|title=Coronavirus: First case confirmed in UAE|website=gulfnews.com|accessdate=2020-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129051659/https://gulfnews.com/uae/health/coronavirus-first-case-confirmed-in-uae-1.1580273983681|archive-date=2020-01-29|url-status=live}}</ref> Shortly afterwards, an [[Emirates (airline)|Emirates]]' news agency confirmed four people from a Chinese family to be infected.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://gulfnews.com/uae/health/coronavirus-in-uae-four-of-a-family-infected-1.1580273983681|title=Coronavirus in UAE: Four of a family infected|website=gulfnews.com|accessdate=2020-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129111625/https://gulfnews.com/uae/health/coronavirus-in-uae-four-of-a-family-infected-1.1580273983681|archive-date=2020-01-29|url-status=live}}</ref> Finland reports its first case of the virus in [[Lapland (Finland)|Lapland]], found in a Chinese tourist who left Wuhan before Wuhan was locked down.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/finlands_first_coronavirus_case_confirmed_in_lapland/11182855|title=Finland's first coronavirus case confirmed in Lapland|date=2020-01-29|publisher=YLE|location=Finland|accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref> Singapore confirms three more cases of the virus, bringing the total infected to 10.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/wuhan-virus-singapore-new-confirmed-cases-coronavirus-12364556|title=Singapore confirms 3 new cases of Wuhan virus; total of 10 infected|accessdate=