ce confirmed a fifth case, the daughter of the patient in the fourth case.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bfmtv.com/sante/coronavirus-en-france-un-cinquieme-cas-confirme-la-fille-du-touriste-chinois-hospitalise-a-paris-1849280.html|title=Coronavirus en France: un cinqui\u00e8me cas confirm\u00e9, la fille du touriste chinois hospitalis\u00e9 \u00e0 Paris|language=French|trans-title=Coronavirus in France: A fith case confirmed, the daughter of a Chinese tourist hospitalised in Paris|work=BFM TV|date=29 January 2020|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130195933/https://www.bfmtv.com/sante/coronavirus-en-france-un-cinquieme-cas-confirme-la-fille-du-touriste-chinois-hospitalise-a-paris-1849280.html|archive-date=30 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nTwo Chinese nationals were placed in isolation wards in [[Armenia]] amid the first suspected case of coronavirus in the country. The Chinese nationals were tourists travelling to Armenia from neighbouring [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]. Liana Torosyan, the head of the Department of Infectious Diseases, advised that samples will be sent to European labs, as Armenia does not have the capacity to test for the novel coronavirus.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1002962.html|title=Two Chinese nationals placed in isolation wards in Armenia amid first suspected case of coronavirus|date=29 January 2020|website=Armenpress.am|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201155551/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1002962.html|archive-date=1 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Brazil reports a total of 9 suspected cases in six states of the country.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://g1.globo.com/bemestar/coronavirus/noticia/2020/01/29/brasil-tem-nove-casos-suspeitos-de-coronavirus-e-33-notificacoes.ghtml|title=Brasil tem 9 casos suspeitos de coronav\u00edrus em 6 estados|publisher=O Globo|location=Brazil|language=Portuguese|website=G1|access-date=2020-02-08|